# Session Log

Cross-session memory for AI agents. Updated at the end of every session
by any agent. Read at the start of every session before any other context.

## Format

```
## YYYY-MM-DD

- [AGENT] Note text
```

Agent identifiers: `[ARCHITECT]` `[BACKEND]` `[FRONTEND]` `[SYSOPS]` `[CYBERSEC]` `[QA]`

Notes should capture:
- Blockers found and their current status
- Informal decisions not yet written as ADRs
- Pending follow-ups for a specific agent or human
- Anything that would otherwise be lost between sessions

Do not duplicate information already captured in a spec, ADR, or tasks.md.

---

## YYYY-MM-DD

- [ARCHITECT] Project session log initialized.
